'''High School of Telecommunication Arts and Technology''' is high school in the neighborhood of [[Bay Ridge, Brooklyn]]. It was formerly [[Bay Ridge High School]]. As Bay Ridge High school it was all girls, but is currently a co-ed high school.<ref name="niche.com">{{cite web|url=https://k12.niche.com/high-school-of-telecommunications-arts--and--technology-brooklyn-ny/|title=High School of Telecommunications Arts & Technology in Brooklyn, NY - Niche|website=IK12.niche.com|accessdate=2016-09-17}}</ref> It is located at 350 67th Street, [[Brooklyn|Brooklyn, NY]] 11220.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://schools.nyc.gov/SchoolPortals/20/K485/default.htm|title=Welcome - High School of Telecommunication Arts and Technology - K485 - New York City Department of Education|website=Schools.nyc.gov|accessdate=2016-09-17}}</ref>  It has a software engineering program.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://insideschools.org/component/schools/school/864|title=High School of Telecommunication Arts and Technology |website=Insideschools.org|accessdate=2016-09-17}}</ref> It has 1300 students.<ref name="niche.com"/> The school is a Gothic style building.<ref name="niche.com"/>

